      "role": "user",
      "content": "Thanks, this is a good start. Could you maybe make it a little bit more personal? Just a touch more warmth so it doesn't feel like a cold template, since they were such a strong contender. Maybe add a line or two acknowledging how difficult these decisions are for the team.",
      "source": "evaluator"
